*FFMinDigitPasscode 10/10: ""
*FFMinDigitPasscode 11/11: ""
*FFMinDigitPasscode 12/12: ""
*CloseUI: *FFMinDigitPasscode

*OpenUI *FFSelectID/Customize User Prompts: PickOne
*DefaultFFSelectID: UserID_AccountID
*FFSelectID UserID_AccountID/Display User ID and Account ID Prompts: ""
*FFSelectID UserID/Display User ID Prompt Only: ""
*FFSelectID AccountID/Display Account ID Prompt Only: ""
*CloseUI: *FFSelectID

*OpenUI *FFEmitPageSizeCommand/Specify Paper size with Print Job Ticket: Boolean
*DefaultFFEmitPageSizeCommand: False
*FFEmitPageSizeCommand False/Not Installed: “”
*FFEmitPageSizeCommand True/Installed: “”
*CloseUI: *FFEmitPageSizeCommand

*%OpenUI *FFEncryptionSetting/Encryption Level: PickOne
*%DefaultFFEncryptionSetting: Current
*%FFEncryptionSetting Current/Current: “”
*%FFEncryptionSetting New/New: “”
*%CloseUI: *FFEncryptionSetting

*CloseGroup: InstallableOptions

